high_descs: Turn around to reach the sidetable.
Pick up the hammer on the right of the table.
Turn to the larger sofa on the right of the table.
Put the hammer on the sofa.
Turn left to the sidetable.
Pick up the hammer on the table.
Turn right to face the larger sofa.
Put the hammer on the sofa next to the other hammer at the far end of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Put two Hammer on the Sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sidetable.
Take the hammer from the table.
Turn around and go near the sofa.
Put the hammer on the corner of the sofa.
Then turn around and go near the sidetable.
Take the hammer from the table.
Then go near the sofa.
Put the hammer on the corner of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Collect the hammer and placed on the corner of the sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sidetable right ahead.
Pick up the hammer from the right side of the table.
Turn towards the sofa on the right of the table.
Place the hammer down on the sofa.
Turn back towards the sidetable.
Pick up the second hammer from the table.
Go back to the same two-seat sofa.
Place the second hammer down on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Place two hammers down on a sofa.
